
For Tk804.025 to build properly on Mac OS X 10.2.6 (Darwin), Perl must
be built dynamic, rather that the default of static.  Use a Configure
incantation similar to this:

sh Configure -des useshrplib=true [-Dprefix=/path/to/your/private/perl]

S. Lidie, 2003/07/31

Another style (knowing nothing of Darwin) might be:

sh Configure -des -Duseshrplib [-Dprefix=/path/to/your/private/perl]

NI-S, 2002/08/04
